---
title: Chicken Gyoza in a Shoyu-Style Broth 2x the delicious portions!
description: Nothing says comfort like homemade soup! You’ll simmer up a sumptuous ramen-style broth infused with ginger and scallions. Add wholesome bok choy, cabbage, peas, and carrots, plus juicy chicken gyoza dumplings. Finish it all with zippy scallion greens and tangy gyoza sauce, and you’re ready to feed a crowd in just 25 minutes!

*This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66df676f48e223afaf60f47e-f9454e98.jpeg
